snippet.title: Office Hustle | Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Office Hustle is a game that focusses on stealth while taking place on a 2D grid. 
Hide from your enemies or lure them away by using objects in the environment. 
Time your moves and use everything in your ability to work yourself up the company in this comedic infiltration game.


On Patrol
Written, recorded and produced by Danya Vodovoz
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNcwZT1x-BUHcWNagbcDccQ
